    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is cooking, pat your <strong>cod fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>cod</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining cayenne pepper </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to marinate – this is your <strong>smoky cod</strong></p>",
