    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) to a bowl with your <strong>mayo</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>aioli</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
