        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>smoky cod</strong> and your <strong>diced chorizo</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook the fish for 4-5 min on each side until the fish is cooked through and the chorizo is crispy – this is your <strong>smoky chorizo cod</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
