        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once the pan is hot, add the <strong>shredded kale</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until wilted and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
