    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong>, <strong>roasted onion</strong> and <strong>roasted pepper</strong> over the <strong>kale</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>smoky chorizo cod</strong> and drizzle the <strong>aioli</strong> all over</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
